charges.charge_description: Complaint &; affidavit in support of arrest &; search warrants. 18:1956(A)(1)(a) Knowing that the property involved in a financial transaction represented the proceeds of some form of unlawful activity, did knowingly &; intentionally conduct such a financial transaction which in fact involved the proceeds of specified unlawful activity with the intent to promote the carrying on of unauthorized redemption of food stamps. Search Warrant: Believed to be located at premises: food stamps, redemption certificates, deposit slips, financial &; business records, ledgers, etc., all of which constitute evidence of violation of 18:1956(a)(1)(A).
